reviewText: This DVD is so poorly done in sound and image quality that it is not worth watching. There is no menu to select Captions The other DVD's, by Norah Jones, are far superior to this one.
NEVER KNEW NORAH JONES UNTIL I HEARD A SAMPLE ON AMAZON -  NOW I THINK I HAVE ALL HER ALBUMS - GREAT VOICE - GOOD ARRANGEMENTS, ETC.....
It was great and very well produced with a great variety of content. Although it was back ordered a couple weeks, it was well worth the wait.
